query:
-- Get or create Orange County agency
INSERT IGNORE INTO counties (name, state, usesStateProtocols, protocolVersion, createdAt)
VALUES ('Orange County EMS Agency', 'California', 0, '2025', NOW());

SET @oc_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Orange County%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Insert Orange County EMS Standing Orders
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
-- Cardiac Standing Orders
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-010', 'Cardiopulmonary Arrest - Adult/Adolescent Non-Traumatic', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Non-Traumatic Cardiac Arrest. CPR, defibrillation, ACLS medications, and airway management.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2021-02-18', 2021, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-015', 'Chest Pain of Suspected Cardiac Origin', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Chest Pain/ACS. 12-lead ECG, aspirin, nitroglycerin, and STEMI activation.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2021-07-15', 2021, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-020', 'Symptomatic Bradycardia - Adult/Adolescent', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Symptomatic Bradycardia. Atropine and transcutaneous pacing.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2024-04-16', 2024, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-025', 'Narrow Complex QRS Tachycardia', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Narrow Complex Tachycardia. Vagal maneuvers and adenosine.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2017-04-01', 2017, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-030', 'Narrow QRS Complex Tachycardia - Irregular Rhythm', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Irregular Narrow Complex Tachycardia. Rate control considerations.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2017-10-01', 2017, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-040', 'Wide QRS Complex Tachycardia with a Pulse', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Wide Complex Tachycardia. Amiodarone and synchronized cardioversion.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2025-04-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-C-045', 'Cardiac Arrest with LVAD', 'Cardiac', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Cardiac Arrest with Left Ventricular Assist Device.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2017-10-01', 2017, NOW()),

-- Environmental Standing Orders
(@oc_id, 'SO-E-005', 'Burn (Thermal, Electrical, Chemical) - Adult', 'Environmental', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Burns. Burn assessment, cooling, and fluid resuscitation.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2024-04-01', 2024, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-E-010', 'Diving - Decompression Sickness / Air Embolism', 'Environmental', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Diving Emergencies. Decompression sickness and air embolism treatment.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2021-09-27', 2021, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-E-015', 'Non-Fatal Drowning', 'Environmental', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Non-Fatal Drowning. Airway management and warming.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2017-04-01', 2017, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-E-025', 'Thermal Disorders', 'Environmental', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Thermal Disorders. Hyperthermia and hypothermia treatment.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2017-04-01', 2017, NOW()),
(@oc_id, 'SO-E-030', 'Snake Envenomation', 'Environmental', 'Orange County EMS Standing Order for Snake Envenomation. Wound care and supportive treatment.', 'https://ochealthinfo.com/providers-partners/emergency-medical-services/ems-policies-procedures-standing-orders/ems-standing', '2018-07-01', 2018, NOW());
